From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: WebKitGTKWin Port <webkitgtkwin@ooblerg.local>
Date: Wed, 17 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] WebKitGTKWin: use OS(WINDOWS) in IPC event semaphore path

GTK-on-Windows has OS(WINDOWS) true but PLATFORM(WIN) false. Use the OS
guard when duplicating the event semaphore so this port takes the Win32Handle
path instead of the UnixFileDescriptor path.
---
 Source/WebKit/Platform/IPC/IPCEvent.h | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/Source/WebKit/Platform/IPC/IPCEvent.h b/Source/WebKit/Platform/IPC/IPCEvent.h
index 8600808..2566fd9 100644
--- a/Source/WebKit/Platform/IPC/IPCEvent.h
+++ b/Source/WebKit/Platform/IPC/IPCEvent.h
@@ -149,6 +149,6 @@ inline std::optional<EventSignalPair> createEventSignalPair()
 {
     Semaphore event;
-#if PLATFORM(WIN)
+#if OS(WINDOWS)
     Semaphore signal(Win32Handle { event.m_semaphoreHandle });
 #else
     Semaphore signal(event.m_fd.duplicate());
-- 
2.45.0
